I think Virgin America right now is
doing an amazing job with their content

00:02:58.940 --> 00:03:00.100
creation and their marketing.

00:03:00.100 --> 00:03:02.600
It's unique, it's original,
it's definitely to their brand.

00:03:02.600 --> 00:03:04.960
I encourage you to check out their
billboards, and their website.

00:03:04.960 --> 00:03:07.720
They've done an amazing job
in creating a fun airline in

00:03:07.720 --> 00:03:09.622
a space where it's really
not a lot of fun to fly.

00:03:09.622 --> 00:03:11.560
When you look at creating a blog and

00:03:11.560 --> 00:03:14.780
a readership there what you really
want to do is have a contact calendar.

00:03:14.780 --> 00:03:17.640
Look out a month or two months of what
you want to write, what you want to

00:03:17.640 --> 00:03:20.290
talk about, and then figure out
how to get that content created.

00:03:20.290 --> 00:03:22.410
So again we're talking
about original content.

00:03:22.410 --> 00:03:24.220
What you want to have is
someone creating it for

00:03:24.220 --> 00:03:26.620
you in a way that tells your story.

00:03:26.620 --> 00:03:29.750
That's the best way to create any
type of sort of blog following.

00:03:29.750 --> 00:03:32.640
I would say when you look at publisher
and social you really have to pay

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:34.580
attention to what channels
you want to engage with and

00:03:34.580 --> 00:03:36.130
have time to engage with.

00:03:36.130 --> 00:03:38.010
When you look at LinkedIn or
Twitter or Facebook,

00:03:38.010 --> 00:03:40.830
which are the three kind of big ones
right now they all have their different

00:03:40.830 --> 00:03:43.420
ways people want to interact, and
they want to hear back from you as well.

00:03:43.420 --> 00:03:47.430
So example on Twitter don't just post
stuff and never go back to it again.

00:03:47.430 --> 00:03:49.330
You want to actually engage
because people will retweet you.

00:03:49.330 --> 00:03:51.110
They'll talk to you, ask you questions.

00:03:51.110 --> 00:03:53.090
Make sure if you do engage in
social you have time to nurture and

00:03:53.090 --> 00:03:54.760
engage that community in the way
